    <name>Portecle</name>
    <summary>Multipurpose keystore and certificate tool</summary>
    <description>
        <p>
            Portecle is a user friendly GUI application for creating,
            managing and examining keystores, keys, certificates, certificate
            requests, certificate revocation lists and more.
        </p>
        <p>
            It makes many common operations with supported cryptographic files
            easy and intuitive compared to for example command line tools with
            hard to remember command syntax.
        </p>
    </description>
